name: Fetch
0:
”Alexa, open Fetch My Calendar”
”Alexa, ask Fetch My Calendar what is happening today”
”Alexa, ask Fetch My Calendar what is happening on Monday”
skdetail:
Rated: Guidance Suggested. This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: fetch my calendar
des:
Fetch hooks up Alexa to your Office 365 calendar events. Just “ask Fetch My Calendar what is happening today”. Fetch will read the subjects and time of your upcoming events.

The Fetch team would love to hear your feedback. Please email us at: squatchsoftware@outlook.com or open an issue at the Fetch GitHub repository https://github.com/squatchsoftware/fetch.
